_sText:
aim_espionage version 2
Made by os-Genome.

CTs start off with 5 smoke grenades nearby. Kill all Ts.

Ts get bunkers. Kill all CTs.

-There is a seperate pitch black escape tunnel leading from CT spawn to T spawn.

-If you use a flashlight, you can be seen.
---

Changes from v1: 
-Reduces spotlight brightness. 
-Added lights in places where Ts could be "invisible" in v1.
-Added pitch black escape tunnel from T to CT spawn.
-Rope to bunker.
-Extra HE and smoke nades near bunker for CTs.
